Just give me a minute. I promise you'll like it.

167
00:09:25,345 --> 00:09:26,629
看
Look.

168
00:09:26,663 --> 00:09:30,473
我已经给你看过了地图 但这还有更多
So I showed you the map already, but there's more,

169
00:09:30,474 --> 00:09:31,934
多得多
a lot more.

170
00:09:31,969 --> 00:09:34,544
我爸的日记巨多
My father had tons of these diaries.

171
00:09:34,556 --> 00:09:36,773
他每月都会写完一本
He filled one up every month.

172
00:09:40,809 --> 00:09:44,995
这么多史料 你找到了我的弱点
So much history. You've found my weak spot.

173
00:09:45,042 --> 00:09:47,457
越往后看就越神秘
They get somewhat more cryptic as it goes on.

174
00:09:47,458 --> 00:09:49,118
到结尾的时候他都开始失控了
He started losing it towards the end.

175
00:09:49,152 --> 00:09:51,186
这是他去世前写的那本
That's the one he was keeping write before he died.

176
00:09:51,204 --> 00:09:53,539
看看最后几页
Check out the last few pages.

177
00:09:57,357 --> 00:09:59,328
"英德尚格波丽"?
"A parching imbued"?

178
00:10:00,697 --> 00:10:02,055
这是什么意思?
What does that mean?

179
00:10:02,367 --> 00:10:05,844
我想这是密码 我感觉这好像和仙宫有关联
I think it's a code. I feel like it's connected to Asgard somehow,

180
00:10:05,845 --> 00:10:09,722
我需要你帮我弄明白它 英格丽德
but I need your help to figure it out, Ingrid.

181
00:10:10,313 --> 00:10:13,059
让我们创造历史吧 我们可以一起做这事
Let's make history. We can do this together.

182
00:10:13,717 --> 00:10:15,399
为什么是我?
Why me?

183
00:10:16,263 --> 00:10:18,597
因为你是女巫
Because you're a witch.

184
00:10:28,635 --> 00:10:30,236
我不是女巫
I'm not a witch.

185
00:10:30,237 --> 00:10:32,247
这里举行慈善活动时我见过你 
I saw you at the charity event right here. 

186
00:10:32,248 --> 00:10:33,970
有个家伙开始对你毛手毛脚
That guy started getting rough with you.

187
00:10:33,971 --> 00:10:36,763
你说了些拉丁语 他的手指就断了
You said some words in Latin. His fingers just broke.

188
00:10:36,764 --> 00:10:40,033
这就是你的证据吗? 想象力真丰富啊
That is your evidence? You have a very vivid imagination.

189
00:10:40,529 --> 00:10:42,618
如果我错了 你为什么逃跑呢?
If I'm wrong, then why are you running away?

190
00:10:42,619 --> 00:10:44,169
我有工作要做!
I have work to do!

191
00:10:59,752 --> 00:11:01,614
嘿 过来
Hey. Come here.

192
00:11:04,151 --> 00:11:06,502
好了 看看这
Okay, check this out.

193
00:11:06,537 --> 00:11:08,588
就在这
Right here.

194
00:11:08,901 --> 00:11:11,736
明天我们就从这开始我们的新生活了
This is where we start our new life tomorrow.

195
00:11:11,886 --> 00:11:15,033
真的要发生了 感觉好不真实 
It just feels so surreal that it's actually happening.

196
00:11:15,034 --> 00:11:18,700
是否感觉我向你求婚是很久之前的事了
Does feel like forever ago when I asked you to marry me.

197
00:11:18,734 --> 00:11:21,069
我可以坦白一下吗?
Can I make a confession?

198
00:11:21,074 --> 00:11:23,567
我从未想过要结婚
I never wanted to get married.

199
00:11:23,715 --> 00:11:25,135
什么?
What?

200
00:11:25,170 --> 00:11:28,722
我总觉得婚姻很... 传统
I just always thought marriage was too... conventional

201
00:11:28,757 --> 00:11:30,808
还很无聊 很平常
and boring and normal.

202
00:11:30,842 --> 00:11:32,959
是人生中任何冒险活动的终结
The end of any adventure in life.

203
00:11:33,079 --> 00:11:36,954
- 我应该担心吗? - 直到我遇见你
- Should I be getting worried? - Until I met you.

204
00:11:37,227 --> 00:11:41,769
然后我意识到婚姻不仅仅是篱笆小院和小货车
And I realized that marriage is more than a picket fence and a minivan.

205
00:11:41,803 --> 00:11:45,272
它是和你爱的人分享你的生活
It's about sharing your life with someone you love.

206
00:11:46,757 --> 00:11:50,703
你知道吗 作为一个环游过世界的人
You know, as someone who's been all over the world,

207
00:11:50,704 --> 00:11:53,497
我... 我实话说
I... I can honestly say,

208
00:11:53,531 --> 00:11:55,783
这一切 当下的这一切...
this, this right here...

209
00:11:55,817 --> 00:11:58,985
这次探险是我最期待的
this is the adventure I'm most looking forward to.

210
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,238
我也是
Me, too.

211
00:12:15,437 --> 00:12:18,425
哟 这不是维克托嘛
Well, well, well, if it isn't Victor.

212
00:12:18,619 --> 00:12:21,587
- 温迪...? - 正是在下
- Wendy...? - In the flesh.

213
00:12:21,971 --> 00:12:23,858
我得多久没见过你了...
Wow. I haven't seen you in...

214
00:12:23,859 --> 00:12:26,067
很久了 别算了
A long time. Let's not put a number on it.

215
00:12:26,068 --> 00:12:27,685
你来这做什么呢 温迪?
So what are you doing here, Wendy?

216
00:12:27,805 --> 00:12:29,806
我以为波尚家族的人都恨我
I thought all the Beauchamps officially hated me.

217
00:12:29,807 --> 00:12:32,659
我们确实恨你 但我们也需要你的帮助
We do officially hate you, but we also need your help.

218
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:33,720
弗雷娅需要你的帮助 
Well, Freya needs your help. 

219
00:12:33,721 --> 00:12:34,888
你还记得弗雷娅是谁吧?
You do remember who Freya is, right?

220
00:12:34,889 --> 00:12:36,939
等下 乔安娜知道你在这吗?  
Wait. Does Joanna know you're here? 

221
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:37,897
我们讨论过这事
We discussed it.

222
00:12:37,932 --> 00:12:39,535
那 出了什么事?  
So, what's the problem?  

223
00:12:39,536 --> 00:12:41,138
弗雷娅失去了她的法力
Freya's lost her powers.

224
00:12:41,139 --> 00:12:43,803
确切地说 某人夺走了它们
Well, to be more precise, somebody's taken them,

225
00:12:43,804 --> 00:12:46,643
我们尝试了一切我们能想到的 除了一件事
and we've tried everything we can think of except one thing.

226
00:12:46,644 --> 00:12:49,639
- 不 不 不 绝对不行 - 让我讲完
- No. No. No. Absolutely not. - Let me finish.

227
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:53,378
我已经很久不行医了也很久没做那种事了
Look, I haven't practiced medicine or done that kind of thing in a long time.

228
00:12:53,748 --> 00:12:57,068
我现在是教授 我更喜欢历史和学术活动
I'm a professor now. I'm more into history, academics.

229
00:12:57,069 --> 00:13:00,038
但我肯定你还记得怎么做
But I'm sure you can remember how to do it.

230
00:13:03,092 --> 00:13:05,038
你知道你在要求什么 对吗?
You do know what you're asking, right?

231
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:07,078
如果这不重要 我就不会来这儿了
I wouldn't be here if it wasn't important.

232
00:13:07,079 --> 00:13:10,481
还有 这里面还有更多的故事 就给我五分钟
Plus, there is way more to the story. Just give me five minutes.

233
00:13:39,945 --> 00:13:41,865
很快了...
Soon...

234
00:14:18,767 --> 00:14:21,319
妈咪嘛咪哄
Reformabit verum.

235
00:14:30,083 --> 00:14:33,620
达什 嘿 我... 我来得有点早了...
Dash, hey. I, uh... I got here a little early...

236
00:14:33,621 --> 00:14:35,488
我在这等着你
I'll just see you when you get here.

237
00:14:39,542 --> 00:14:44,454
妈咪嘛咪哄
Veniat ad me metalli.

238
00:14:45,065 --> 00:14:49,093
妈咪嘛咪哄
Veniat ad me metalli.

239
00:14:49,281 --> 00:14:51,053
加德纳夫人?
Mrs. Gardiner?

240
00:14:51,071 --> 00:14:53,889
艾米 你怎么来了?
Amy. What are you doing here?

241
00:14:53,907 --> 00:14:55,557
达什约了我在这见面
I'm supposed to be meeting Dash.

242
00:14:55,575 --> 00:14:57,559
我真心觉得你不该碰那东西
I really don't think you should touch that.

243
00:14:57,577 --> 00:14:59,995
为什么? 你觉得这很危险吗?
Why? Do you think it's dangerous?

244
00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:02,314
很有可能 我们还不知道那是什么
It might be. We don't know what it is.

245
00:15:02,315 --> 00:15:04,111
达什和我一直在调查 但...
Dash and I have been investigating, but...

246
00:15:04,112 --> 00:15:06,671
事实上 它是种毒药
Actually, it's a poison,

247
00:15:06,690 --> 00:15:10,382
它是从另一个世界渗透穿墙而来的
and it's seeping through the wall from another world.

248
00:15:10,383 --> 00:15:13,012
有这个可能
That's certainly a theory. 

249
00:15:13,013 --> 00:15:14,847
这是个事实 亲爱的
It's a fact, dear.

250
00:15:15,128 --> 00:15:18,247
好在 它对凡人是致命的
Good thing, it's lethal to mortals.

251
00:15:40,026 --> 00:15:41,871
艾米?
Amy?

252
00:16:13,597 --> 00:16:16,496
妈妈 天呐 你吓我一跳 你怎么来了?
Mom. Oh, my God, you scared me. What are you doing here?

253
00:16:16,497 --> 00:16:19,152
我不是你的母亲
I'm not your mother.

254
00:16:19,186 --> 00:16:21,020
妈咪嘛咪哄
Mitte.

255
00:16:26,643 --> 00:16:29,516
天呐 请别这样
Oh, God, please. Don't.

256
00:16:29,719 --> 00:16:33,750
- 救命! 不! - 闭... 嘴
- Help! No! - Shut... up.

257
00:16:37,882 --> 00:16:39,332
真漂亮
So pretty.

258
00:16:39,522 --> 00:16:42,375
天呐
Oh, my God.

259
00:16:42,376 --> 00:16:45,995
帮我给你母亲带个话儿
Give your mother a message from me.

260
00:16:47,331 --> 00:16:50,731
妈咪嘛咪哄
Per mortem argenteum.

261
00:17:09,903 --> 00:17:11,058
弗雷娅?
Freya?

262
00:17:11,059 --> 00:17:13,002
妈妈 假冒者刚来过酒吧
Mom. The shifter was just here at the bar.

263
00:17:13,003 --> 00:17:14,824
- 你没事吧? - 嗯 我没事
- Are you okay? - Yeah, I'm all right.

264
00:17:14,858 --> 00:17:17,526
她刚走 我还可以看到她 她到第四街道去了
She just left, though. I can see her. She's headed down Fourth Street.

265
00:17:17,544 --> 00:17:19,329
待在弯曲手肘
Stay at the Bent Elbow.

266
00:18:29,817 --> 00:18:32,068
那 你怎么看? 你能做吗?
So, what do you think? Can you do it?

267
00:18:32,102 --> 00:18:33,423
能 不过很危险 
Yes, but it's dangerous, 

268
00:18:33,424 --> 00:18:35,571
我们需要乔安娜参与才能完成
and we need Joanna to pull it off.

269
00:18:35,764 --> 00:18:38,802
没有她的话能完成吗?
Ooh. Um, can we do it without her?

270
00:18:38,803 --> 00:18:41,544
这样就容易多了 我能代替她吗?
I mean, it would be so much easier. Can I do it for her?

271
00:18:41,578 --> 00:18:43,586
不 必须得是乔安...
No, it has to be Joann...

272
00:18:45,949 --> 00:18:47,417
温迪?
Wendy?

273
00:18:47,451 --> 00:18:50,549
- 怎么? - 你跟我说她知道我要来
- What? - You told me she knew I was coming.

274
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:53,425
不 我没说 我说我们讨论过了
No, I didn't. I said that we discussed it.

275
00:18:53,459 --> 00:18:56,327
讨论的结果是她不让我找你
And the discussion ended with her telling me not to find you.

276
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:58,968
- 她什么时候回来? - 我不知道
- When is she getting back? - I don't know.

277
00:18:58,969 --> 00:19:01,140
不如你在我屋子里等等吧
But it might be a good idea for you to wait in my room.

278
00:19:01,141 --> 00:19:03,033
我可能需要慢慢告诉她 不 等等!
I might need to break it to her gently. No, wait! Oh.

279
00:19:03,034 --> 00:19:05,952
- 这根本不是个好主意 - 你不能走
- This is not a good idea at all. - You can't leave.

280
00:19:05,953 --> 00:19:08,705
你向我保证过 我们说好了的
You made me a promise. We had a deal.

281
00:19:08,898 --> 00:19:11,068
现在到我屋里去!
Now go to my room!

282
00:19:33,303 --> 00:19:35,868
迈克 我们要关门了 你得走了
Mike. We're closed. You need to leave.

283
00:19:35,869 --> 00:19:37,408
"英德尚格波丽." 我知道这是什么意思
"A parching imbued." I know what it means.

284
00:19:37,409 --> 00:19:39,546
- 我不关心 - 这是字母易位词
- I don't care. - It's an anagram.

285
00:19:39,547 --> 00:19:40,256
你该走了  
It's time for you to leave.  

286
00:19:40,257 --> 00:19:41,912
它的意思是"英格丽德・波尚"
It means "Ingrid Beauchamp."

287
00:19:41,913 --> 00:19:44,631
我不知道你在说什么 我也不想知道
I don't know what you're talking about, and I don't want to know.

288
00:19:44,632 --> 00:19:46,558
要是你改变"英德尚格波丽"的字母顺序
If you rearrange the letters of "A Parching Imbued,"

289
00:19:46,559 --> 00:19:48,990
就可以拼出你的名字... 英格丽德・波尚
it spells your name... Ingrid Beauchamp.

290
00:19:49,029 --> 00:19:52,174
我跟你说了 我们要关门了 你得马上离开
I told you. We are closed. You need to leave right now.

291
00:19:52,175 --> 00:19:53,564
问题是 在我父亲的日记里
Question is, why would my father 

292
00:19:53,565 --> 00:19:55,417
为什么会有你名字的字母易位词呢?
have an anagram of your name in his diary?

293
00:19:55,418 --> 00:19:57,456
- 好了 我要叫警察了 - 不 你不会的
- Okay, I'm gonna call the police. - No, you're not.

294
00:19:57,457 --> 00:19:59,191
上次在图书馆被我赶走的那个家伙
What did you say happened to the last guy

295
00:19:59,192 --> 00:20:00,304
还记得他怎么样了... 
who cornered me in the library... 

296
00:20:00,305 --> 00:20:01,231
他的手指怎么样了吗?
something about broken fingers?

297
00:20:01,232 --> 00:20:02,743
一点儿不差 因为你用咒语做到的 
Exactly, 'cause you broke it with a spell, 

298
00:20:02,744 --> 00:20:03,499
因为你就是个女巫
because you are a witch.

299
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,851
好了 你在骚扰我 我要叫警察了
Okay. Now you're harassing me. I'm calling the police.

300
00:20:05,852 --> 00:20:08,091
要是你承认事实 我们就可以继续了
If you just admit the truth, we can move on.

301
00:20:08,092 --> 00:20:10,456
- 我不是女巫! - 我知道你在隐藏秘密
- I am not a witch! - I know you're sworn to secrecy.

302
00:20:10,471 --> 00:20:13,005
我父亲连续几年研究你们的文化 我知道密码
My father studied your culture for years. I know about the code.

303
00:20:13,006 --> 00:20:15,740
根本没有密码! 我不知道你在说什么
There is no code! I don't know what you're talking about.

304
00:20:15,741 --> 00:20:17,348
好吧
Fine.

305
00:20:20,214 --> 00:20:21,568
我来证明一下
I'll prove it.

306
00:20:22,264 --> 00:20:23,882
天哪!
Oh, my God!

307
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:26,828
迈克!
Mike!

308
00:20:28,437 --> 00:20:33,036
我觉得特别无助 太恐怖了
I just felt completely defenseless. It was awful.

309
00:20:33,037 --> 00:20:35,322
然后她告诉我给你捎个信
And then she told me to give you a message.

310
00:20:35,323 --> 00:20:37,424
妈咪嘛咪哄?
Per mortem argenteum?

311
00:20:37,730 --> 00:20:39,852
什么? 这是什么意思?
What? What does that mean?

312
00:20:39,853 --> 00:20:42,035
意思是我们得恢复你的能力
It means we need to get your powers back.

313
00:20:42,036 --> 00:20:44,047
可是你和温迪都说了这是不可能的啊
But you and Wendy both said there was no way.

314
00:20:44,048 --> 00:20:46,713
还有一种可能
Mm, there's still one possibility.

315
00:20:49,010 --> 00:20:52,296
这太疯狂了! 你为什么要这么做?!
This is insane! Why are you doing this?!

316
00:20:52,330 --> 00:20:55,899
你得马上把我治好 要不我就会流血致死了
You need to heal me right now, or I'm gonna bleed to death.

317
00:20:56,242 --> 00:20:57,279
我知道你能做到... 
I know you can do it... 

318
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,505
每个女巫都有疗伤的能力
every witch has healing power.

319
00:20:58,506 --> 00:21:00,971
我不会治好你 你才不关心你的死活
I'm not healing you. I don't care if you die.

320
00:21:00,972 --> 00:21:03,106
你应该不想向警察解释这些吧
I don't think you want to explain this to the police.

321
00:21:03,141 --> 00:21:05,721
你能解释啊! 我要打911!
You can explain it! I'll just call 911!

322
00:21:05,722 --> 00:21:07,857
医务人员到这里之前我就死了
I'll be dead before the paramedics get here.

323
00:21:07,891 --> 00:21:10,200
求你... 治好我吧
Just... heal me.

324
00:21:10,201 --> 00:21:13,355
- 你疯了 你知道吗? - 我已经决定了
- You are insane, do you know that? - I'm determined.

325
00:21:13,553 --> 00:21:16,116
我到这里来是找去仙宫的路 
I came here to find the way to Asgard, 

326
00:21:16,117 --> 00:21:17,892
来完成我父亲的工作
to finish my father's life work.

327
00:21:17,893 --> 00:21:20,311
不过没有你我做不到
But I can't do it without you.

328
00:21:20,405 --> 00:21:22,424
我需要你 英格丽德
I need you, Ingrid.

329
00:21:22,686 --> 00:21:25,104
求你了 不要让我在这里死掉
Please, don't let me die here.

330
00:21:33,274 --> 00:21:35,380
我以前从没有治疗过别人 
I've never even healed anyone before. 

331
00:21:35,381 --> 00:21:36,961
我不确定这有没有用
I'm not sure if this will work.

332
00:21:36,995 --> 00:21:38,629
至少 我们在进步了...
We're making some progress, at least...

333
00:21:38,664 --> 00:21:41,248
- 你已经承认了 - 我没承认
- You're admitting something. - I admit nothing.

