你在想什么呢 弗雷娅?
What were you thinking, Freya?

514
00:31:51,951 --> 00:31:54,477
我想和我的父亲在一起
I was thinking I wanted to spend time with my father.

515
00:31:54,650 --> 00:31:56,985
维克托 我想你该离开
Victor, I think you should leave.

516
00:31:57,036 --> 00:31:59,006
我觉得弗雷娅的彩排晚宴
I just don't think that Freya's rehearsal dinner 

517
00:31:59,007 --> 00:32:00,976
不是个修补关系的好时间
is the right time to reconnect.

518
00:32:01,001 --> 00:32:03,590
拜托? 就像你说的 这是我的彩排晚宴
Hello? Like you said, it's my rehearsal dinner.

519
00:32:03,621 --> 00:32:05,382
要是我想他在这里 他就可以在这里
If I want him to stay, he can stay.

520
00:32:05,383 --> 00:32:07,228
我要辩解一下 乔安娜 
In my defense, Joanna, 

521
00:32:07,229 --> 00:32:09,409
我今天过来 不是仅仅露个面
I was brought here today. I didn't just show up.

522
00:32:09,410 --> 00:32:11,529
既然我来了 我至少应该和她们说说话
But now that I'm here, I should at least be able to speak to them.

523
00:32:11,530 --> 00:32:13,027
她们也是我的孩子  
They're my children, too.  

524
00:32:13,028 --> 00:32:14,524
除非她们不会跟你说话
Not if they don't want to speak to you.

525
00:32:14,525 --> 00:32:17,766
- 我 我想 - 为什么?
- l, I would like to speak to him. - Why?

526
00:32:17,767 --> 00:32:20,659
你去哪里了? 我指的不止是这一世
Where have you been? And I don't just mean in this life.

527
00:32:20,660 --> 00:32:23,538
我看过无数过去的照片...一个都没有你
I've seen tons of pictures from the past... you're not in any of them.

528
00:32:23,539 --> 00:32:25,699
- 英格丽德 我能解释的 - 对不起
- Ingrid, I can explain. - I'm sorry.

529
00:32:25,700 --> 00:32:27,934
我不想听你的解释
I don't want to hear your explanations.

530
00:32:28,427 --> 00:32:30,897
嘿 各位 只有我和加德纳一家在
Hey, guys. It's getting kind of weird back there 

531
00:32:30,898 --> 00:32:31,885
显得有点奇怪呢
with just me and the Gardiners.

532
00:32:31,886 --> 00:32:33,716
嘿 你回来了
Oh, hey. You're back.

533
00:32:34,298 --> 00:32:36,735
我要去上菜了
I have to get dinner on the table.

534
00:32:51,059 --> 00:32:53,310
我知道你来不是你自己的意思
I know it wasn't your idea to come here.

535
00:32:53,325 --> 00:32:55,960
很抱歉 妈妈和英格丽德那样对你
I'm sorry for the way Mom and Ingrid are being.

536
00:32:55,994 --> 00:32:57,962
没事的 弗雷娅
It's okay, Freya.

537
00:32:57,996 --> 00:32:59,681
她们有她们的原因
They have their reasons.

538
00:32:59,715 --> 00:33:01,832
如果我是她们 也不会想跟我说话了
If I were them, I wouldn't talk to me either.

539
00:33:01,850 --> 00:33:06,675
我能... 给你看样东西吗?
Hey. Can I... show you something?

540
00:33:12,811 --> 00:33:16,259
我知道我离开了 但是我... 我有努力
I know I've been gone but I... I do keep up.

541
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:18,261
尽我所能
As best I can.

542
00:33:19,568 --> 00:33:22,203
我不理解
I don't understand.

543
00:33:22,237 --> 00:33:24,038
你离开了我们
You left us.

544
00:33:24,510 --> 00:33:28,012
但我离开并不是因为不爱你
Uh... but I didn't leave because I didn't love you.

545
00:33:29,211 --> 00:33:31,656
弗雷娅 亲爱的 你要错过晚饭了
Freya, sweetie, you're missing your dinner.

546
00:33:31,657 --> 00:33:34,006
我想... 单独跟你爸爸谈谈
And I'd like to... talk to your father alone.

547
00:33:40,756 --> 00:33:42,178
乔安娜 我没有...  
Look, Joanna, I don't...  

548
00:33:42,179 --> 00:33:42,890
不 听我说
No, just listen.

549
00:33:42,925 --> 00:33:46,728
弗雷娅不需要再接近你然后再次被抛弃
Freya does not need to get close to you only to be abandoned again.

550
00:33:46,762 --> 00:33:49,981
我没有抛弃任何人
I did not abandon anyone.

551
00:33:50,015 --> 00:33:52,216
你就是这样跟她们说的吗?
Is that what you told them?

552
00:33:52,234 --> 00:33:54,530
我还能怎么说呢?
Well, what should I have told them?

553
00:33:56,794 --> 00:34:00,640
- 我现在不能这么做 - 乔安娜...
- I can't do this now. - Joanna...

554
00:34:10,569 --> 00:34:12,136
宝贝
Babe.

555
00:34:12,755 --> 00:34:14,572
你好吗?
You okay?

556
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:17,575
很好 不好意思 我只是在屋里有点压抑
Yeah. Sorry. It's just a little overwhelming in there.

557
00:34:17,593 --> 00:34:19,427
我想象的到
I can imagine.

558
00:34:19,461 --> 00:34:21,929
我只想透透气
I just needed to get outside.

559
00:34:21,964 --> 00:34:24,081
我们去走走吧?
Why don't we go somewhere?

560
00:34:24,099 --> 00:34:25,226
什么意思?  
What do you mean? 

561
00:34:25,227 --> 00:34:27,802
好啦 我们走吧 就... 你和我
Come on. Let's go. Just... you and me.

562
00:34:28,730 --> 00:34:30,330
我们一起去冒险吧
Let's start our adventure together.

563
00:34:41,596 --> 00:34:44,952
- 一切都还好吗? - 不 不好
- Is everything okay? - No. Not really.

564
00:34:44,987 --> 00:34:46,621
一点都不好
Not at all.

565
00:34:49,107 --> 00:34:53,205
我知道你爸爸在这儿...
I know your dad being here...

566
00:34:53,627 --> 00:34:56,931
我没心情听那个人的借口
I'm not in the mood for this man's excuses.

567
00:34:57,774 --> 00:34:59,300
你知道吗?
You know?

568
00:34:59,334 --> 00:35:01,469
他错过了他的机会
He missed his chance.

569
00:35:08,541 --> 00:35:10,247
温迪
Wendy.

570
00:35:10,604 --> 00:35:12,764
我能单独跟英格丽德谈谈吗?
Can I speak to Ingrid alone, please?

571
00:35:17,065 --> 00:35:18,903
英格丽德...
Ingrid...

572
00:35:20,773 --> 00:35:24,492
她不会那么容易原谅你 相信我
Yeah. That one doesn't forgive so easy. Take it from me.

573
00:35:30,449 --> 00:35:32,817
在海边的时候 我总会感觉好点
I always feel better when I'm by the ocean.

574
00:35:32,835 --> 00:35:36,454
海那么广阔 让我的问题看起来很渺小
It's so big. It makes my problems feel small.

575
00:35:36,488 --> 00:35:38,456
应该说是我们的问题
Well, now they're our problems.

576
00:35:40,826 --> 00:35:44,178
要是你没办法改变的事呢?
What if it's something you can't fix?

577
00:35:44,213 --> 00:35:46,180
还没有这样的事
No such thing.

578
00:35:46,215 --> 00:35:48,466
- 我是个医生 - 我是认真的
- I'm a doctor. - I'm serious.

579
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:50,802
我是说 看看我的爸妈
I mean, look at my parents.

580
00:35:50,836 --> 00:35:53,805
他们深爱着彼此 我看的出来
They loved each other. I know they did.

581
00:35:53,839 --> 00:35:58,776
但是... 那还不够 他们还是会分开
But... it's not always enough. It can still fall apart.

582
00:35:58,811 --> 00:36:02,113
不论你多么爱一个人 他们还是会离开的
No matter how much you love someone, they can still walk away.

583
00:36:02,147 --> 00:36:05,182
我不会离开你的 永远不会
I won't walk away from you. Ever.

584
00:36:05,200 --> 00:36:07,685
我打赌我爸妈也跟彼此说过这样的话
I bet my parents told each other the same thing.

585
00:36:07,686 --> 00:36:11,323
他们不能在一起不代表我们也一定会分开
Just because it didn't work for them doesn't mean that it won't for us.

586
00:36:11,487 --> 00:36:14,473
这是... 你必须做的选择 
It's... a choice you have to make, 

587
00:36:14,474 --> 00:36:16,394
就是你哪儿也不会去
that you're not going anywhere.

588
00:36:16,829 --> 00:36:20,464
即使这个选择很难 尤其是确实很难的时候
Even when it gets hard. Especially when it gets hard.

589
00:36:20,499 --> 00:36:23,384
我保证我每天都会做出这样的选择
I promise you I will make that choice every day.

590
00:36:24,703 --> 00:36:27,639
我和你对抗整个世界
It's you and me against the world.

591
00:36:28,090 --> 00:36:29,807
好吗?
Deal?

592
00:36:30,318 --> 00:36:31,893
好
Deal.

593
00:36:37,182 --> 00:36:40,217
该把你送回家了
We should probably get you home soon.

594
00:36:40,235 --> 00:36:43,187
对啊 该回去了
Yeah. Probably should.

595
00:36:50,612 --> 00:36:53,414
我得说我想念你的聚会了
I got to say I missed your... your parties.

596
00:36:53,448 --> 00:36:56,527
你做的饭 还有...
And your cooking. And, uh...

597
00:36:56,745 --> 00:36:58,569
还有你
And you.

598
00:37:01,239 --> 00:37:03,591
乔安娜 无论如何
Joanna, for what it's worth,

599
00:37:03,625 --> 00:37:06,427
你都一个人做了一件...
you know, you've done a...

600
00:37:06,461 --> 00:37:08,596
非常棒的事
Pretty great job on your own.

601
00:37:08,630 --> 00:37:10,443
这所有的一切
With everything.

602
00:37:11,780 --> 00:37:15,193
我无法想象你经历了多少困难
I can't imagine how hard it must've been on you.

603
00:37:15,721 --> 00:37:17,889
谢谢你
So thank you.

604
00:37:17,923 --> 00:37:21,058
谢谢你照顾好我们的女儿
Thank you for taking such good care of our girls.

605
00:37:21,092 --> 00:37:24,929
不客气 谢谢你能这么说 维克托
You're welcome. Thank you for saying that, Victor.

606
00:37:24,947 --> 00:37:28,933
你或许不相信我 但是我仍然想你
You probably don't believe me, but I... I still think about you.

607
00:37:28,951 --> 00:37:31,435
每天
Every day.

608
00:37:31,869 --> 00:37:36,073
但是你一直知道我在哪儿 我们在哪儿
And yet you've always known where I am. Where all of us are.

609
00:37:36,367 --> 00:37:39,212
你知道我从来没有停止过爱你 
You know I never stopped loving you. 

610
00:37:39,213 --> 00:37:41,245
那不是我们分开的原因
That wasn't what drove us apart.

611
00:37:46,168 --> 00:37:49,470
我试着用几个轮回的时间来忘记你
I've tried for centuries to forget you.

612
00:37:49,504 --> 00:37:51,622
但那没用
It doesn't work.

613
00:37:54,238 --> 00:37:56,685
当我见到你 我仍然...
When I see you, I still...

614
00:37:58,925 --> 00:38:00,765
维克托...
Victor...

615
00:38:14,043 --> 00:38:15,652
英格丽德
Ingrid.

616
00:38:18,367 --> 00:38:20,580
迈克 你怎么找到我的?  
Mike, how did you find me here? 

617
00:38:20,581 --> 00:38:22,453
我是个探索者 记得吗?
I'm an explorer, remember?

618
00:38:22,487 --> 00:38:24,505
我查了一下电话簿
I explored a phone book.

619
00:38:24,539 --> 00:38:28,175
你不能就这么出现在我家 你有什么事?
You can't just show up at my house. Why are you here?

620
00:38:28,210 --> 00:38:30,921
有件事我需要跟你说
There's something I need to talk to you about.

621
00:38:31,981 --> 00:38:34,302
我知道通往仙宫的门在哪儿 
I know where the door to Asgard is. 

622
00:38:34,303 --> 00:38:36,267
我还知道怎么通过那道门
And I know how to get through.

623
00:38:36,301 --> 00:38:38,469
没办法过去的
There's no way through.

624
00:38:38,503 --> 00:38:41,522
只有一把钥匙 但是被毁了
There was only one key, and it was destroyed.

625
00:38:41,556 --> 00:38:42,861
那个巨蛇座吗? 
The serpens clavem? 

626
00:38:42,862 --> 00:38:45,309
是的 我还有其他办法 英格丽德
Yeah, I know some things, too, Ingrid.

627
00:38:45,681 --> 00:38:48,379
还有第二把钥匙 这就是我想告诉你的
There's a second key. This is what I've been trying to tell you.

628
00:38:48,413 --> 00:38:52,316
- 它在哪儿? - 不是哪儿 而是谁
- Where is it? - Not where. It's who.

629
00:38:53,106 --> 00:38:54,986
是你 英格丽德
It's you, Ingrid.

630
00:38:55,516 --> 00:38:58,522
"英德尚格波丽"就是另一把钥匙
"A parching imbued" is the other key.

631
00:38:58,540 --> 00:39:01,993
你就是那把钥匙 你要帮我打开它
You're the other key. And you're gonna help me open it.

632
00:39:12,004 --> 00:39:14,638
这跟我想的一样吗?
Is that what I think it is?

633
00:39:15,232 --> 00:39:16,700
这个镇子唯一的隧道就是
The only tunnels in this town 

634
00:39:16,701 --> 00:39:18,169
费尔黑文下面的地下墓穴
are the catacombs under Fair Haven.

635
00:39:18,170 --> 00:39:19,810
我想不出来还会是什么
I don't know what else it could be.

636
00:39:19,845 --> 00:39:22,234
我以为它是要给我们看假冒者是谁
Well, I thought it was supposed to show us who the shifter is.

637
00:39:22,235 --> 00:39:23,885
本来是的
It was.

638
00:39:25,567 --> 00:39:27,143
我不知道这是什么意思 
I don't know what this means.  

639
00:39:27,144 --> 00:39:28,719
那我们就要想办法弄明白
Well, we need to figure it out.

640
00:39:28,737 --> 00:39:31,405
弗雷娅明天要在那里结婚
Freya's getting married there tomorrow.

641
00:39:50,042 --> 00:39:53,051
我终于要杀了她了 爸爸
I'm finally going to kill her, Father.

642
00:39:54,898 --> 00:39:57,349
然后我就回家
And then I'm coming home.

643
00:40:45,296 --> 00:40:47,648
你来干什么?
What are you doing here?

644
00:40:47,682 --> 00:40:49,501
我来跟你说再见
I couldn't leave without saying good-bye.

645
00:40:52,491 --> 00:40:54,326
我爱上你了
I'm in love with you.

646
00:40:57,025 --> 00:40:58,215
- 什么? - 跟我走 
- What? - Come with me. 

647
00:40:58,216 --> 00:40:59,108
我们今晚就可以离开
We can leave tonight.

648
00:40:59,109 --> 00:41:00,817
等等 你不能这么想  
Wait. Y... You need to stop.  

649
00:41:00,818 --> 00:41:02,525
我们属于彼此 你知道的
We belong together. You know we do.

650
00:41:02,531 --> 00:41:05,983
这太疯狂了 我明天要跟达什结婚了
This is crazy. I am marrying Dash tomorrow.

651
00:41:06,001 --> 00:41:09,587
你不能嫁给达什 你只会被他占有
You can't marry Dash. You'll just become another one of his possessions.

652
00:41:09,621 --> 00:41:11,488
我们之间是不会变成那样的  
It wouldn't be like that with us. 

653
00:41:11,489 --> 00:41:13,090
没有什么"我们" 基利安
There is no "us," Killian.

654
00:41:13,125 --> 00:41:14,825
在遇见我之前你梦到我了
You dreamt about me before you met me.

655
00:41:14,843 --> 00:41:16,093
我也梦到你了
I dreamt about you, too.

656
00:41:16,128 --> 00:41:17,898
我都不敢相信你是真实存在的 
I didn't even think you existed 

657
00:41:17,899 --> 00:41:19,532
直到我在订婚晚会上遇见你
until I met you at that engagement party.

658
00:41:19,533 --> 00:41:22,133
我的整个人生 我以为我一直在逃避
My whole life, I thought I was running away

659
00:41:22,167 --> 00:41:24,435
所有人 所有事
from everyone, everything.

660
00:41:24,970 --> 00:41:26,770
但是现在我知道...
But now I know I was...

661
00:41:27,016 --> 00:41:29,017
这一切都是为了遇见你
Just running toward you.

662
00:41:31,309 --> 00:41:36,307
我爱你 在遇见你之前就爱上你了
I love you. I loved you even before I met you.

663
00:41:43,304 --> 00:41:45,922
你嫁给他 会毁了你的
You marry him, it'll destroy you.

